channel.title: Comments on: Corona Geek On Air – Episode 13 – Hanging out with Dean Murphy, Joke Shake app developer

item.title: By: charlesmckeever
item.dc:creator: charlesmckeever
item.description: Dean's working on his first game app. He's shared a few video walk throughs with me and I have to say I really like his style of clean and simple UI. The menu system for his next app has an organic fell and is playful, which makes you want to interact with it right from the beginning. I'm looking forward to seeing it in the app store.
